        "startIntroPart1": "Hail, Warlord of the Blade, master of discipline and steel! When the old world shattered, your people did not crumble with it. They sharpened their weapons, tightened their ranks, and forged a code of honor from the ashes. The Blade is feared across the wasteland not for cruelty, but for absolute martial perfection. Your warriors fight without hesitation, your smiths forge the finest weapons from salvaged steel, and no wounded fighter of the Blade has ever stopped fighting.",
