        "startIntroPart1": "All hail the Oracle of the Seers, reader of the patterns and planner of the long game! While other factions stumble from crisis to crisis, your people see further. The Seers track the cycles of the wasteland - the radiation storms, the migration patterns, the rise and fall of rival factions - and they plan accordingly. Your settlement was built not where survival is easiest today, but where it will be safest a generation from now. The Oracle's predictions have saved your people time and again, and the other factions come to you when they need to know what is coming.",
